summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of the Alley in Block 2, Craven's Division of Greenlake Addition, being the Alley between North 68th Street and North 70th Street from Fremont Avenue to Linden Avenue, and certain other streets, avenues and alleys, by paving and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 6071, and appropriating money from the City Street Fund in aid thereof.
